> Keep in mind that when using this resource along with
[<span pulumi-lang-nodejs="`acme.Certificate`" pulumi-lang-dotnet="`acme.Certificate`" pulumi-lang-go="`Certificate`" pulumi-lang-python="`Certificate`" pulumi-lang-yaml="`acme.Certificate`" pulumi-lang-java="`acme.Certificate`">`acme.Certificate`</span>][resource-certificate] within the same configuration, a
